title: [Gyldemar Forest, The Barrens]
description: A pale white tree, leaning against a gigantic boulder, now stands upside down with its roots in the air.  Bits of wood fan out from the tree to the north.

A pale white tree, leaning against a gigantic boulder, now stands upside down with its roots in the air.  Bits of wood fan out from the tree to the north.  The darkness of the barrens seems to become even darker here.
